('woocommerce_admin_notice_wc_zapier_new_user','<div class=\"wc-zapier-notice wc-zapier-notice-new-user\"><h2>Welcome to Zapier Integration for WooCommerce!</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Explore the Power of Data:</strong> Instantly connect and manage Orders, Products, Coupons, Customers, Subscriptions, Bookings, Memberships, and more.</li>\n	<li><strong>70+ Triggers:</strong> Unleash your creativity with precise control over when and how your WooCommerce data flows to Zapier.</li>\n	<li><strong>25+ Actions:</strong> Effortlessly create, find, and update WooCommerce data directly from your Zaps.</li>\n	<li><strong>Stay Ahead of the Curve:</strong> Enjoy full support for the latest WooCommerce features, including High Performance Order Storage (HPOS) and the sleek new Cart and Checkout Blocks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n<a class=\"button button-primary\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://docs.tectalic.com/woocommerce-zapier/quick-start/?utm_source=woocommerce&amp;utm_medium=plugin&amp;utm_campaign=welcome\">Quick Start</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"button\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://docs.tectalic.com/woocommerce-zapier/?utm_source=woocommerce&amp;utm_medium=plugin&amp;utm_campaign=welcome#whats-new\">What\'s New</a></p>\n</div>','auto'),
